thread.title: John Andrew Townend
thread.title_full: Rentalcars.com reviewed by John Andrew Townend

author: John Andrew Townend
title: John Andrew Townend
text: We have rented cars in Florida for the past 10 years & nearly every time we have used rentalcars.com. Each year we look at alternative suppliers but generally we come back to rentalcars.com because they offer us the most efficient service & more importantly the best price.
